# 🌍 Travel Recommendation Web App

A dynamic travel recommendation web application that allows users to search destinations and display filtered results using JavaScript and JSON data.

## 🚀 Live Demo

https://mcchiquito.github.io/travelRecommendation/

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript (DOM Manipulation)
* JSON Data Handling

## ✨ Features

* Destination search functionality
* Dynamic rendering of travel recommendations
* Data filtering using JavaScript
* Interactive UI updates
* Responsive layout
* Clean navigation structure

